        protected void initCredentials()
        Description copied from class: AnekaProvider
        Sets the values of AnekaProvider.url, AnekaProvider.username, AnekaProvider.password, AnekaProvider.appName. This method will be called when attached to the ExecutionManager in order to provide a way to change the credentials in response to a UI event. After the new credentials are set, a login will be started.
